rows.label: bf09130100_0010
rows.name: Your Holiness, the foes have been sighted.

rows.label: bf09130100_0020
rows.name:
The lost technology of old Iira?
How astounding it is that it still works...

rows.label: bf09130100_0030
rows.name:
Surprised, eh?
There are still a few of us hanging on.

rows.label: bf09130100_0050
rows.name:
Man-Eater.
You followed him down that dark path.

rows.label: bf09130100_0090
rows.name:
Oh, nice try!
But that's not gonna work on me!

rows.label: bf09130100_0100
rows.name:
And that's because
you and I are the same!

rows.label: bf09130100_0140
rows.name:
The Blade Eater technology is not known
outside the Holy See!

rows.label: bf09130100_0160
rows.name: But that doesn't mean you're the only one.

rows.label: bf09130100_0170
rows.name:
Or have you forgotten what you did before
implanting your Core Crystal?!
